Description: Rockpalast proudly presents: One of the many legendary concerts that have been requested over and over.

U2 live in 1981 at Metropolitan in Berlin. One of the first concerts of the Irish in Germany, full of their early hits, including 'Gloria', 'I Will Follow' and 'Eleven O'Clock Tic-Toc'.

Honestly, this is probably the best video of U2 in the early 80's. I've seen a lot, and most are crap. This one is very clear, well shot, awesome sound. A must for any U2 fan. Fuck you Henry Rollins.
